{"tid":1611641,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民建聯陳克勤：警員受襲擊挑釁開槍自衛合理","createTime":"2019-10-02T04:17:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T06:17:40.000Z","uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"d0210740bfe26c6c5addb70fa0ef6ec05af999bb","tid":1611641,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:17:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1483823-20191002.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1483823-20191002.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=9ZkxwAQN0Q6nkyzE8ymhdGa%2FpyP0knsd4enDGc0qzPM%3D&h=c3f83a99\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1483823-20191002.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=058ead24\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1483823-20191002.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n建制派回應衝突 陳克勤：警員受襲擊挑釁開槍自衛合理<br />\n2019-10-02 HKT 11:00<br />\n <br />\n建制派回應衝突 陳克勤：警員受襲擊挑釁開槍自衛合理<br />\n在北京，出席完國慶活動的建制派立法會議員聯合見記者，回應昨日多區發生的嚴重衝突。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯的陳克勤認為，警員昨日受暴徒襲擊及挑釁，因而自衞開槍，是合情、合理、合法、合規的做法，又認為示威者暴力不斷升級，建議政府研究引用《緊急法》止暴制亂。陳克勤又指出，激進示威者在舉天同慶的日子作出破壞，漠視對國家及全國人民的尊重，對他們的行徑表示遺憾，令港人蒙羞，予以最嚴厲譴責，建議政府應盡快開展多次對話平台，虛心聆聽意見，解決問題。 <br />\n<br />\n經民聯的梁美芬說，政府應使用所有法律手段，包括考慮成立特別法庭，研究如何速審速判涉及反修例示威的案件，亦要求政府增加警方及律政司的資源，加快檢控工作。<br />\n<br />\n工聯會的黃國健說，工聯會多個辦事處昨日受到破壞，相信是政治攻擊，與11月區議會選舉有直接關係，要求政府提出可行措施，保障選舉是公平合理地進行。"},{"pid":"62b4be977c2266322f03594e83b57df415e7f7e0","tid":1611641,"uid":134071,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:17:40.000Z","msg":"而家仲有人話寧願放生建制派, 都要整死泛民?"},{"pid":"02ce25ef8afc146e4eb959da1535a914d48cbea1","tid":1611641,"uid":259141,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:22:53.000Z","msg":"等仆街啦, 民賤聯"},{"pid":"2e10e5eb5f0d7ce52553e04627b4140736b9e66e","tid":1611641,"uid":251581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:23:50.000Z","msg":"建制派根本唔入流 <br />\n元秋，搓breast勤都做到議員就知<br />\n總之 區議會  一票都不投建制派"},{"pid":"5dd842b44b7519c58b9b38e48c4253fe1f888b56","tid":1611641,"uid":41458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:24:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5914d8c8d19fcb9ad4db9c6af24bb60d130ea27d","tid":1611641,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:24:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2b6b2bf533e8ff39af249163780e3319e265a134","tid":1611641,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:24:58.000Z","msg":"制裁名單"},{"pid":"a5b0c3a47cc3823f7a37b5e5fc35c62979531afc","tid":1611641,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e10e5eb5f0d7ce52553e04627b4140736b9e66e","tid":1611641,"uid":251581,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:23:50.000Z","msg":"建制派根本唔入流 <br />\n元秋，搓breast勤都做到議員就知<br />\n總之 區議會  一票都不投建制派"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:26:36.000Z","msg":"而家建制派不斷要求取消區議會選舉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3258bbfa85f3a836352ea0d0f81efbb4cadba057","tid":1611641,"uid":74244,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:26:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ea3cdb1f9a55410f8da